292
00:14:58.791 --> 00:15:02.666
вЂЄDid you love him
вЂЄbecause he was such a good husband to you?

293
00:15:03.541 --> 00:15:07.875
вЂЄOr did you love him because
вЂЄhe was a great father to my sister?

294
00:15:09.500 --> 00:15:12.125
вЂЄBut it's okay. We are here now.

295
00:15:14.166 --> 00:15:15.666
вЂЄThe secret is out. fine.

296
00:15:17.833 --> 00:15:19.500
вЂЄ-Where is he?
вЂЄ-I'll smack you.

297
00:15:19.583 --> 00:15:20.625
вЂЄ-You're being disrespectful now.
вЂЄ-Oh?

298
00:15:20.708 --> 00:15:22.916
вЂЄYou know. old lady. what I don't want?

299
00:15:23.541 --> 00:15:25.666
вЂЄI don't want my sister to end up like me.

300
00:15:26.875 --> 00:15:29.791
вЂЄTo become an alcoholic because of you.

301
00:15:30.750 --> 00:15:33.750
вЂЄAnd I definitely
вЂЄdon't want her to end up like you.

302
00:15:34.958 --> 00:15:39.166
вЂЄSolving all her problems by running
вЂЄto garbage men and spreading her legs.

303
00:15:39.750 --> 00:15:41.000
вЂЄListen.

304
00:15:41.083 --> 00:15:43.541
вЂЄYou're being
вЂЄvery disrespectful now. disrespectful.

305
00:15:43.625 --> 00:15:45.250
вЂЄGo ahead and hit me. old lady.

306
00:15:46.500 --> 00:15:48.041
вЂЄIt doesn't hurt anymore.

307
00:15:51.833 --> 00:15:52.916
вЂЄLater.

308
00:15:55.458 --> 00:15:56.458
вЂЄ[Freedom sniffles]

309
00:15:59.125 --> 00:16:00.166
вЂЄ[door closes]

310
00:16:05.333 --> 00:16:06.750
