313
00:16:13.125 --> 00:16:14.541
вЂЄThey're on holiday.

314
00:16:15.291 --> 00:16:16.791
вЂЄWhat about Ntombi?

315
00:16:18.125 --> 00:16:21.375
вЂЄNtombi took the last born
вЂЄto his grandmother.

316
00:16:21.958 --> 00:16:23.375
вЂЄIt's just you and I.

317
00:16:23.458 --> 00:16:24.666
вЂЄNo one else is here.

318
00:16:25.250 --> 00:16:26.666
вЂЄYou knowвЂ¦ [sighs]

319
00:16:27.791 --> 00:16:32.625
вЂЄвЂ¦what I refuse to do
вЂЄis leave you all alone in a hotel.

320
00:16:33.375 --> 00:16:34.541
вЂЄat a time like this.

321
00:16:35.250 --> 00:16:38.291
вЂЄ[inhales sharply] Here's what I'll do.
вЂЄI'll take care of you.

322
00:16:38.958 --> 00:16:40.500
вЂЄI'll make some soft porridge.

323
00:16:41.291 --> 00:16:44.291
вЂЄ-You'll make me porridge? [chuckles]
вЂЄ-I will make you porridge.

324
00:16:44.375 --> 00:16:45.708
вЂЄRegain your strength.

325
00:16:47.875 --> 00:16:49.250
вЂЄ[Joyce] <i>вЂЄWhere is that key?</i>

326
00:16:49.791 --> 00:16:51.000
вЂЄ[phone chimes]

327
