вЂЄ-Whoa. Mom.
вЂЄ-Hmm?

328
00:16:55.250 --> 00:16:56.333
вЂЄWhat's going on?

329
00:16:57.916 --> 00:16:59.250
вЂЄLindani's been discharged. Ma.

330
00:16:59.791 --> 00:17:01.458
вЂЄI shouldn't have agreed
вЂЄto come with you guys.

331
00:17:01.541 --> 00:17:03.041
вЂЄOh. come on.

332
00:17:03.125 --> 00:17:05.833
вЂЄ-She's with her mom though. right?
вЂЄ-And what difference will she make?

333
00:17:06.791 --> 00:17:08.458
вЂЄShe's not very supportive.

334
00:17:09.541 --> 00:17:12.958
вЂЄWait. wait. Just hold on.
вЂЄWhat are you saying? Is Lindani okay?

335
00:17:13.041 --> 00:17:14.458
вЂЄShe was in hospital.

336
00:17:15.041 --> 00:17:17.333
вЂЄBut Mpume says she's been discharged.

337
00:17:17.416 --> 00:17:20.041
вЂЄWhy? WhaвЂ¦ What happened?

338
00:17:22.375 --> 00:17:24.375
вЂЄ-Say something!
вЂЄ-Gosh. Menzi.

339
00:17:24.458 --> 00:17:26.833
вЂЄShe was pregnant and had a miscarriage.

340
00:17:26.916 --> 00:17:28.833
вЂЄ-Goodness.
вЂЄ-[dramatic music playing]

341
00:17:28.916 --> 00:17:30.625
вЂЄ[distorted] But she'll be fine.

342
00:17:33.791 --> 00:17:35.458
вЂЄ[distorted] Menzi. are you okay?

343
00:17:36.666 --> 00:17:40.541
вЂЄ-[hyperventilating]
вЂЄ-Oh. my God. What's going on? Menzi.

344
00:17:40.625 --> 00:17:44.333
вЂЄ-[straining]
вЂЄ-Menzi. breathe. Breathe!

345
00:17:49.916 --> 00:17:53.125
вЂЄ[Joyce] You should've stayed over at the
вЂЄhospital and had the doctor check on you.

346
00:17:53.208 --> 00:17:55.333
вЂЄ[Menzi] No. Mom. the doctor said I'm fine.

347
00:17:55.416 --> 00:17:56.708
вЂЄIt was just a panic attack.

348
00:17:56.791 --> 00:17:59.250
вЂЄOf course you will say it
вЂЄlike it was nothing.

349
00:17:59.333 --> 00:18:00.833
вЂЄWe've never seen you like that.

350
00:18:00.916 --> 00:18:02.583
вЂЄ[Joyce] Thank you. The day isn't over.

351
00:18:02.666 --> 00:18:05.291
вЂЄ-I'm thinking. let's watch a movie.
вЂЄ-Oh.

352
00:18:05.375 --> 00:18:06.916
вЂЄ-And enjoy the rest of the dayвЂ¦
вЂЄ-Ma.

353
00:18:07.000 --> 00:18:08.541
вЂЄ-вЂ¦since we didn't leave.
вЂЄ-Yes.

354
00:18:08.625 --> 00:18:11.666
вЂЄSo let's make some popcorn
вЂЄand chill together.

355
00:18:11.750 --> 00:18:13.625
вЂЄ-You'll pick something great. right?
вЂЄ-Mm-mmm.

356
00:18:13.708 --> 00:18:14.708
вЂЄ-[Joyce] Hmm?
вЂЄ-Horror.

357
00:18:14.791 --> 00:18:17.333
вЂЄNo. you'll scare him
вЂЄinto another panic attack.

358
00:18:17.416 --> 00:18:18.625
вЂЄ-[scoffs]
вЂЄ-[laughs]

359
00:18:18.708 --> 00:18:20.583
вЂЄ-Your mom with the bad jokes.
вЂЄ-[Joyce] I'm sorry.

360
00:18:20.666 --> 00:18:21.833
вЂЄ-[Menzi] Wow.
вЂЄ-Let's go. bro.

361
00:18:23.958 --> 00:18:25.666
вЂЄ[Mpume laughing]

362
00:18:27.708 --> 00:18:29.625
вЂЄ[Lindani]
вЂЄThis has been so difficult for me.

363
00:18:30.375 --> 00:18:31.375
вЂЄ[Jonasi] I know.

364
00:18:31.458 --> 00:18:34.000
вЂЄ-[tense music playing]
вЂЄ-[Lindani] But it's okay. I will heal.

365
00:18:34.083 --> 00:18:38.166
вЂЄAnd I'll give birth to more babies
вЂЄfor you. and have a family.

366
00:18:38.250 --> 00:18:39.458
вЂЄ[Lindani. Jonasi chuckle]

367
00:18:40.125 --> 00:18:42.750
вЂЄ[Lindani] I'll be your fourth wife
вЂЄand we'll have a family.

368
00:18:42.833 --> 00:18:45.583
вЂЄ-[Jonasi chuckles]
вЂЄ-[Lindani] Maybe we'll have twins.

369
00:18:45.666 --> 00:18:47.083
вЂЄ-[chuckles]
вЂЄ-[Jonasi] Twins?

370
00:18:50.583 --> 00:18:51.958
вЂЄ[Jonasi] My love.

371
00:18:52.458 --> 00:18:53.791
вЂЄ[suspenseful music playing]

372
00:19:00.083 --> 00:19:01.500
вЂЄ[Lindani] I feel good now.

373
00:19:02.416 --> 00:19:04.666
вЂЄThis will pass. Hmm?

374
00:19:05.416 --> 00:19:07.958
вЂЄ-I know. Thank you for taking care of me.
вЂЄ-[grunts]

375
00:19:08.541 --> 00:19:09.541
вЂЄ[gasps]

376
00:19:10.833 --> 00:19:11.916
вЂЄJoyce.

377
00:19:12.875 --> 00:19:13.875
вЂЄMs Joyce.

378
00:19:15.208 --> 00:19:17.208
вЂЄWhat bullshit is this?

379
00:19:19.208 --> 00:19:20.291
вЂЄThis is a child.

380
00:19:21.666 --> 00:19:24.625
вЂЄ-You're the father of her baby?
вЂЄ-[Jonasi] No. Listen. Joyce.

381
00:19:24.708 --> 00:19:28.166
вЂЄYou are the-the father of the baby

382
00:19:28.250 --> 00:19:30.375
вЂЄ-Lindani miscarried. Jonasi?
вЂЄ-Let me explain. Wait.

383
00:19:30.458 --> 00:19:32.250
вЂЄWhat are you explaining?
вЂЄWhat are you doing?

384
00:19:32.333 --> 00:19:33.875
вЂЄ-Joyce. wait.
вЂЄ-What are you doing? Hey!

385
00:19:33.958 --> 00:19:35.625
вЂЄ-Leave me alone.
вЂЄ-Let me explain. Listen.

386
00:19:35.708 --> 00:19:37.541
вЂЄWhat the hell
вЂЄdo you wanna explain. Jonasi?

387
00:19:37.625 --> 00:19:38.750
вЂЄ-Explain what?
вЂЄ-Listen to what I'm saying.

388
00:19:38.833 --> 00:19:40.375
вЂЄ-Joyce. No. Wait. Wait.
вЂЄ-You're sleeping with a child!

389
00:19:40.458 --> 00:19:42.083
вЂЄThere's nothing to explain about that.

390
00:19:42.166 --> 00:19:43.291
вЂЄDon't tell me what to do!

391
00:19:43.375 --> 00:19:44.708
вЂЄ-What the hell is up with you?
вЂЄ-Ow! Joyce!

392
00:19:44.791 --> 00:19:47.125
вЂЄ-[Lindani] Ms Joyce!
вЂЄ-You're not going anywhere! Lindani!

393
00:19:47.208 --> 00:19:49.208
вЂЄ-Ms Joyce! Ms Joyce!
вЂЄ-Wait. You're going to hurt her.

394
00:19:49.291 --> 00:19:51.125
вЂЄJoyce. Calm down. Joyce. stop!

395
00:19:51.208 --> 00:19:54.083
вЂЄ-No. Jonasi! Let me go. let me go!
вЂЄ-Joyce! Stop it. Joyce!

396
00:19:54.166 --> 00:19:56.250
вЂЄ-No. Joyce. no!
вЂЄ-[Lindani] What are you doing?

397
00:19:56.333 --> 00:19:58.583
вЂЄ-Joyce. stop it!
вЂЄ-Lindani!

398
00:19:58.666 --> 00:20:02.750
вЂЄCalm down. please! Joyce! Joyce. wait!
вЂЄJoyce! You're going to hurt her! Stop it!

399
00:20:02.833 --> 00:20:06.083
вЂЄ-Help me. Jonasi! [screams]
вЂЄ-You're gonna hurt her! Calm down!

400
00:20:06.166 --> 00:20:07.583
вЂЄHey. hey. hey. Let go of me.

401
00:20:07.666 --> 00:20:09.583
вЂЄ-Menzi. Menzi!
вЂЄ-Hey. Don't touch me.

402
00:20:09.666 --> 00:20:11.708
вЂЄ-Hey. leave her alone. Leave her.
вЂЄ-You're sleeping with your own daughter?

403
00:20:11.791 --> 00:20:13.416
вЂЄYou are sleeping with your own daughter!

